*2013 ECMA Nomination Song of the Year for “Beat this Heart”, Co-written with [[Tim Chaisson]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ottawalife.com/2014/06/bring-sunshine-to-your-day-with-days-of-rain/|title= Bring Sunshine to Your Day with Days of Rain |publisher=Ottawa Life |date=2014-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-06}}</ref>

